  "subject": "Fix nssmf-adapter runtime crash",
  "commit_message": "Fix nssmf-adapter runtime crash\n\n- exclude blueprint-proto dependency since it pulls in kotlin\n  dependencies that lead to an incomplete class path during the runtime\n- add @SpringBootTest that tests spring context and catches such issues\n- bump snapshot version to 1.11.1-SNAPSHOT\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4237\nChange-Id: Idae8628a9dc743498faa9082641468654112d9a7\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
